{%- assign featured_product = collections['all'].products.first -%}

<section class="landing-hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <span class="hero-badge">Digital therapy resource</span>
    <h1>CBT Worksheets Mega Bundle</h1>
    <p>
      Our CBT worksheets mega bundle has been developed for professionals supporting people living with anxiety,
      depression, OCD, ADHD, insomnia, addiction, chronic pain, and eating disorders who can benefit from
      CBT-based therapy. Equip every session with evidence-informed exercises that translate complex concepts into
      practical, client-ready tools.
    </p>
    <ul class="hero-list">
      <li>Worksheets, cards, and journals designed for one-on-one or group therapy</li>
      <li>Adaptable resources for common presentations including anxiety, depression, ADHD, OCD, and more</li>
      <li>Instant digital download with professional licensing for clinical use</li>
    </ul>
    {% if featured_product %}
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div class="product-price">
          <span class="price-label">Bundle price</span>
          <strong>{{ featured_product.price | money }}</strong>
          {% if featured_product.compare_at_price_max > featured_product.price %}
            <small>({{ featured_product.compare_at_price_max | money }} value when purchased separately)</small>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="/cart/add" class="product-form" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ featured_product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}">
          <button type="submit" class="button button-primary" {% unless featured_product.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>
            {% if featured_product.available %}
              Add bundle to cart
            {% else %}
              Sold out
            {% endif %}
          </button>
        </form>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ featured_product.url }}">View product details</a>
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <p class="hero-meta hero-meta--fallback">
        Add the bundle to your store catalog to enable purchasing from the homepage.
      </p>
    {% endif %}
    <p class="hero-guarantee">
      Please note that there is overlap in the exercises across the bundle due to every strategy being CBT-based.
      Each worksheet has been adapted with examples and prompts tailored to the specific condition it serves.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    {% if featured_product and featured_product.featured_image %}
      <img
        src="{{ featured_product.featured_image | img_url: '720x720' }}"
        alt="{{ featured_product.featured_image.alt | default: featured_product.title | escape }}"
        class="hero-product-image"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    {% else %}
      <div class="hero-placeholder">
        <span class="placeholder-badge">Mega bundle preview</span>
        <h3>140+ ready-to-print pages</h3>
        <p>Session planners, guided journals, psychoeducation one-pagers, and homework assignments.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="hero-rating">
      <span class="rating-stars" aria-hidden="true">â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…</span>
      <div class="rating-copy">
        <strong>4.9 / 5 stars</strong>
        <p>Trusted by therapists, coaches, and mental health students worldwide.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-section">
  <div class="feature-intro">
    <h2>Built for professionals who need ready-to-use CBT interventions</h2>
    <p>
      Deliver consistent, confident care with printable and digital resources you can tailor to each client. Every
      worksheet is organized so you can quickly brief clients, capture insights, and assign meaningful follow-up
      work with minimal prep time.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Session-ready structure</h3>
      <p>Clear step-by-step prompts guide clients through cognitive restructuring, behavioural activation, and
        thought logging exercises.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Versatile formats</h3>
      <p>Download, print, or use digitally with editable PDF formats to match the needs of telehealth or in-person
        sessions.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Professional polish</h3>
      <p>Consistent design language and colour palettes reinforce your brand while keeping psychoeducation easy to
        digest.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

